&quot;Who is right, who can tell, and who gives a damn right now/ I got the spirit lose the feeling let it out somehow.&quot; - Joy Division


In the news recently, Avril is apparently breaking up with her latest hubby, the left-hanging Chad Kroeger. 

Chad is only still the leader of the band in the clubhouse voted the world's number one musical turnoff. Indeed in May 2013, the readers of Rolling Stone magazine named Nickelback the second worst band of the 1990s, behind only Creed.

Per uk.celebrity.yahoo, Chad passed on attending Avril's recent 30th birthday celebration out on the town. &quot;The couple have apparently unfollowed each other on social media as well - a definite sign in modern Hollywood that things are over.&quot; 

Turn out the lights, let's get this party started right.

The sun sets as well during Av's set at Summer Sonic, so there is a nice light and shadow show contrast to the little night music blast.

And oh yeah, she's still got it. She can still be so damn cute. She can still work a crowd. And with a voice! She can still sing (better than just about anybody).

Praise the pop-rock goddesses that bring the motherfuckin princess bliss. 

What the hell were you thinkin, what the hell yeah. In deed and word thought out throughout the land. Ain't it grand to be alive and well and living in your own Moulin Rouge heaven. 

With your girlfriend to be feeling free.

